  <brief_title>Radiotherapy or Imiquimod in Complex Lentigo Maligna</brief_title>
  <acronym>RADICAL</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised Controlled Multicentre Trial of Imiquimod Versus Radiotherapy for Lentigo Maligna (LM) When Staged Surgical Excision With 5mm Margins is Not Possible, is Refused, or Fails</official_title>
